Open source project. License - GNU GPL 3.0. Feel free to re-use project code. Learn more on GitHub: https://github.com/Ho1Ai/jelly-editor

Standard names template:
- variables - snake_case
- labels - snake_case
- constants (const and #define) - CAPS_CASE
- functions - camelCase
- structures (structs) - PascalCase
- filenames - kebab-case
- catalog names - kebab-case
